These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
Movie-Genre: thriller, zombie
Sport: baseball, sailing
1. Movie-Genre:zombie is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:thriller##3
2. Sport:sailing is on the right of Movie-Genre:zombie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | thriller |
| Sport       | baseball | sailing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
Cigar: tiparillo, blend
Job: musician, security-guard
1. Job:security-guard is on the left or right of Cigar:blend##3
2. Cigar:blend is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | blend |
| Job      | security-guard     | musician  |

 #################################
 
